Sentencas: Microtubular solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated by the multi-dip coating of ceramic aqueous slurries on steel wire.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of LSCF-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC microtubular SOFCs prepared by multi-dip coating

Sentencas: This is a very convenient way to make small straight tubes without requiring special handling.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of LSCF-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC microtubular SOFCs prepared by multi-dip coating

Sentencas: Prepared NiO-GDC/GDC double layered tubes were separated by dissolving the pre-coated polystyrene layer in organic solvent, then were sintered at 1350 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of LSCF-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC microtubular SOFCs prepared by multi-dip coating

Sentencas: Then a cathode layer of LSCF-GDC was also formed on the double layered tubes with heat treatment at 1100 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of LSCF-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC microtubular SOFCs prepared by multi-dip coating

Sentencas: The prepared microtubular cell performs with a maximum power density of 0.34 W/cm(2) at 550 degrees C. Microstructure observation of the tubes suggested the possibility of further improvement, in cell quality.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of LSCF-GDC/GDC/NiO-GDC microtubular SOFCs prepared by multi-dip coating
